#, no-wrap
msgid "Benefits"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: guide/transaction-spec/principles/benefits.adoc:6
msgid ""
"The invoice and credit note provides simple support for complex invoicing, "
"where there is a need for credit note in addition to an invoice. Other "
"potential benefits are, among others:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: guide/transaction-spec/principles/benefits.adoc:8
msgid ""
"Can be mandated as a basis for national or regional eInvoicing initiatives."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: guide/transaction-spec/principles/benefits.adoc:9
msgid ""
"Procurement agencies can use them as basis for moving all invoices into "
"electronic form. The flexibility of the specifications allows the buyers to "
"automate processing of invoices gradually, based on different sets of "
"identifiers or references, based on a cost/benefit approach."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: guide/transaction-spec/principles/benefits.adoc:10
msgid ""
"SME can offer their trading partners the option of exchanging standardised "
"documents in a uniform way and thereby move all invoices/credit notes into "
"electronic form."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: guide/transaction-spec/principles/benefits.adoc:11
msgid ""
"Large companies can implement these transactions as standardised documents "
"for general operations and implement custom designed bi-lateral connections "
"for large trading partners."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: guide/transaction-spec/principles/benefits.adoc:12
msgid "Supports customers with need for more complex interactions."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: guide/transaction-spec/principles/benefits.adoc:13
msgid ""
"Can be used as basis for restructuring of in-house processes of invoices."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: guide/transaction-spec/principles/benefits.adoc:13
msgid ""
"Significant saving can be realised by the procuring agency by automating and "
"streamlining in-house processing. The accounting can be automated "
"significantly, approval processes simplified and streamlined, payment "
"scheduled timely and auditing automated."
msgstr ""
